commit.message:
re PR libstdc++/56278 (unordered containers fail static assertion)

	PR libstdc++/56278
	* include/bits/hashtable_policy.h (_Hash_code_base): Make default
	constructor public.
	* testsuite/23_containers/unordered_set/56278.cc: New.

From-SVN: r195935
